        <div class="scenery">
            <h3><em>Scenery</em></h3>
            <p>Fall brings cooler temperatures and beautiful colors as the mountain peaks gain a new dusting of snow and the aspens turn from green to gold.</p>
            <div class="scenery-container">
                <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mightyamazon67/Fall-in-love-with-RMN/main/DSCF1404.JPG">
