        </div>
        <div class="closing">
            <p>Close enough to Denver to be a fun daytrip; far enough away to feel like you're getting away from it all.  Come for a day, or stay for a few in lovely,quaint Estes Park.  Perhaps a stay at the world famous Stanley Hotel?</p>
            <div class= "img">
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mightyamazon67/Fall-in-love-with-RMN/main/stanley%20hotel%20edit.jpg">
